  "title": "Chewy Indulgent Citrusy Uruguayan Stir-fry",
  "description": "A unique and indulgent dish featuring citrusy flavors with a chewy texture, incorporating oregano for depth in this egg-free-friendly Uruguayan recipe.",
  "cuisine": "Uruguayan",
